title: Two area high school football teams land a spot in the Plays of the Week
text:
Two area high school football teams land a spot in the Plays of the Week 
Updated: Mon, Oct 19 2015, 01:43 PM 
Stream WZTV Fox 17 Newscasts LIVE starting with Fox 17 This Morning at 4:30am, News at 5:30pm and News at 9pm & 10 pm 

The Friday Night Rivals game on our sister station turned in a couple of memorable performances during Week 9 of the high school football season. 
See which players from Blackman and Siegel landed a spot in our Plays of the Week with Paul Jones and Dave Foster.
